      <title>美国抵押贷款利率回升至 7% 以上，融资活动放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/us-mortgage-rates-push-back-above-7-slowing-financing-activity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国抵押贷款利率上周回升至7%以上，导致购房融资申请数量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/us-mortgage-rates-push-back-above-7-slowing-financing-activity</guid>
