    <item>
      <title>西南航空启动权益计划以回应 Elliott 的入股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/southwest-starts-rights-plan-in-response-to-elliott-taking-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西南航空公司表示，已采取权利计划，旨在防止在不向其他股东提供补偿的情况下出现所谓的对该航空公司的“事实上或负面控制”，以回应激进投资者埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 增持该公司股份的行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/southwest-starts-rights-plan-in-response-to-elliott-taking-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:57:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球最大核聚变项目成本飙升且延期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/costs-jump-at-world-s-biggest-nuclear-fusion-project-with-delays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大规模聚变能实验的测试将推迟数年，预计将产生数十亿美元的额外成本，这对这个原本就造价高昂的项目来说无疑是雪上加霜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/costs-jump-at-world-s-biggest-nuclear-fusion-project-with-delays</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三菱日联金融集团收购印度消费贷款公司股权的谈判据称遭遇阻碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/mufg-s-talks-for-stake-in-india-consumer-lender-said-to-hit-snag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，三菱日联金融集团 (Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group Inc.) 就 HDFC 银行有限公司 (HDFC Bank Ltd.) 消费贷款部门少数股权的谈判因对公司战略的话语权存在分歧而陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/mufg-s-talks-for-stake-in-india-consumer-lender-said-to-hit-snag</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:51:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Scope 称法国大选结果可能对评级造成压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-vote-outcomes-will-probably-pressure-rating-scope-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据Scope Ratings称，周日法国大选决选中最有可能出现的两种结果都将损害修复其公共财政的努力，并有可能对欧洲产生更广泛的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-vote-outcomes-will-probably-pressure-rating-scope-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:51:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
