      <title>中国提出让私人债权人在早期债务重组谈判中发挥作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/china-floats-private-creditors-role-in-early-debt-rework-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国提议私人债权人参与发展中经济体债务重组谈判的早期阶段，以加快往往陷入分歧的复杂谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/china-floats-private-creditors-role-in-early-debt-rework-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:08:32 GMT</pubDate>
